headline: Fox Corporation Executives to Discuss Fourth Quarter and Full Year Fiscal 2025 Financial Results Via Webcast
summary: Fox Corporation (Nasdaq: FOXA, FOX) will discuss fourth quarter and full year financial results for the 2025 fiscal year ended June 30, 2025, via a live audio webcast beginning at 8:30 a.m. ET / 5:30 a.m. PT on August 5, 2025.

headline: What You Need to Know Ahead of Fox Corporation’s Earnings Release
summary: Fox Corporation is gearing up to report its fiscal fourth-quarter earnings next month, with analysts anticipating a modest double-digit increase in profitability.
